      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIENVENUE (3) is trending the right way, improving last start to be 0.8L off the winner after getting well back in the run. The inside draw this time around is a big tick and Purton remaining in the saddle is a good push for his chances. Can go one better this time around. SIGHT HERMOSO (4) finished 2.5L off the winner last time out at Sha Tin and comes to this course for the first time. He'll need a touch of luck from the barrier, but he's shown plenty of talent early in his career. There's no reason why he can't get back to winning ways. JUMBO TREASURE (2) has the speed to roll across from barrier seven and lead as he has done in recent efforts. He's been strong from the front his past few and if he's able to dictate from the front, he'll be right in the mix once again. IGOR STRAVINSKY (8) hasn't been far away in recent runs and can make his presence felt once again.",
